# Mirrorr — Docker build ignore list
# Prevents large/unnecessary files from being sent to the Docker build context

# Build outputs (copied selectively in Dockerfile stages)
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/.next
**/coverage

# Dev data — never include in image
data/
infra/dev/
infra/prod/.env

# Dependencies — rebuilt in Docker stages
**/node_modules

# Dev environment files
infra/dev/.env
infra/dev/.env.*
!infra/dev/.env.example
infra/prod/.env
!infra/prod/.env.example

# Logs and temp files
**/*.log
**/*.log.*
tmp/

# VCS and tooling
.git
.gitignore
.github/
.vscode/
.idea/

# Docs and tests (not needed at runtime)
docs/
**/tests/
**/coverage/
**/vitest.config.*
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts

# Misc
README.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
DISCLAIMER.md
ROADMAP.md
